c: 29
v: 40
t: "Kala maษ“ษ“e, Men leptirno junuubi mun ษ—in: no e maษ“ษ“e, ษ“e Men wuurti henndu e mun; no e maษ“ษ“e, ษ“e haacaango halki; no e maษ“ษ“e, mo Men mutini ษ—um ka leydi, no e maษ“ษ“e kadi, ษ“e Men yoolunoo. Kono non, Alla siforaali tooรฑoowo ษ“e; si ko woni, ko kamษ“e tooรฑunoo ko'e maษ“ษ“e"